---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms — PhoneHub"
  description="PhoneHub terms of service. Understand the terms governing your use of our platform."
>
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mb-8">Last updated: July 2026</p>

    <div class="glass-card p-6 md:p-8 space-y-6 text-gray-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        By accessing and using PhoneHub ("the Service"), you agree to the following terms and conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, please discontinue use of the site.
      </p>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Use of the Service</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>PhoneHub is provided <strong class="text-gray-200">free of charge</strong> for personal, non-commercial use. You may browse product information, read reviews, use the comparison tool, and access news content.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>You agree <strong class="text-gray-200">not to scrape, crawl, or automate access</strong> to PhoneHub in a manner that could harm the service or violate the rights of other users.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-accent-blue mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>You agree not to use PhoneHub for any unlawful purpose or in violation of any applicable laws or regulations.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Data Accuracy Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          Product specifications, prices, and other information on PhoneHub are provided <strong class="text-gray-200">"as-is"</strong> and are aggregated from third-party sources including GSMArena, manufacturer websites, and other databases. While we strive for accuracy, we <strong class="text-gray-200">cannot guarantee</strong> that all information is complete, current, or error-free. Always verify critical specifications from the manufacturer or retailer before making a purchase decision.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">AI-Generated Content</h2>
        <p>
          Some content on PhoneHub, including but not limited to product reviews, summaries, and recommendations, is generated with the assistance of artificial intelligence. AI-generated content <strong class="text-gray-200">may contain errors, inaccuracies, or biases</strong>. It should not be considered as professional advice. PhoneHub does not endorse any specific product or brand based on AI-generated analysis.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
        <p>
          PhoneHub participates in affiliate programs with retailers including Amazon, Flipkart, and others. When you click on product links and make a purchase, we may earn a commission at no additional cost to you. This does not influence our product listings, reviews, or ratings. For full details, see our <a href="/phonehub/disclosure" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">Affiliate Disclosure</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the fullest extent permitted by law, PhoneHub and its operators shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, or any loss of profits or revenues, whether incurred directly or indirectly, arising from your use of the service. This includes, but is not limited to, damages resulting from reliance on product information, incorrect specifications, or purchasing decisions made based on content on this site.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>
          Product names, logos, and images displayed on PhoneHub are the property of their respective owners and are used for identification and informational purposes only. The PhoneHub name, design, and original content are proprietary. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works from PhoneHub's original content without prior written permission.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">External Links</h2>
        <p>
          PhoneHub contains links to external websites and retailers. We are not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or terms of service of any third-party websites. Clicking on external links is at your own discretion and risk.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Changes to Terms</h2>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated date. Continued use of PhoneHub after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For questions about these terms, please visit our <a href="/phonehub/contact" class="text-accent-blue hover:underline">contact page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
